name: Toya Selaka Waterfall

This place like hidden Gem because the view from cliff so natural. Water is vrry fresh and clean on  small river surounding by green trees.  So you Guys if you looking the real natural waterfall.. You have to come and feel the nature  of Toya selaka Waterfall.
